# Project Structure (App Router)

```
app/
  layout.tsx
  page.tsx
  loading.tsx
  error.tsx
  not-found.tsx
  (routes)/
components/
lib/
store/
hooks/
styles/
```

- Route segments use lowercase with dashes
- Colocate route-specific components inside route folders
- Shared components go in `/components`
- Server utilities go in `/lib`
